problem and\nits performance is compared with several benchmarks. Numerical experiments\nconfirm the promise of this indirect design approach for task-oriented\nmulti-agent communications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 May 2020 18:29:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Jul 2021 14:27:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 16 Aug 2021 12:14:53 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 31 Jan 2022 11:31:07 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 4 Jan 2023 14:13:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-05"}
