earch, we have publicly released all the well-labelled COVID-19\nthemed apps (and malware) to the research community. Till now, over 30 research\ninstitutes around the world have requested our dataset for COVID-19 themed\nresearch.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 May 2020 15:21:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 13 Feb 2021 15:28:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 18 Apr 2021 04:18:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-20"}
